GOVERNMENT ORDER NUMBER: GRASSANA-0525 / P.No.66 / GRA No.4
Martyr Rajguru Chowk, Madam Cama Marg,
1. Department of Food, Civil Supplies and Consumer Protection, Government Decision No. September 22, 2025
The judicial work of all the District Consumer Grievance Redressal Commissions in the state is done impartially and
In accordance with the provision of the Government Decision in question, to be carried out in a transparent manner, Shri. Madhuri krishtnaji
Atmanade, the member, is replaced by his name in front of the column no. The commission shown in section 4 is being done.
2. By order of this Government, Shri. Madhuri Krishnaji Atmande, Member, District Consumer Grievance Redressal
Commission, Gadchiroli. Deactivating from 23.02.2026 (M.No.). Mr. Atmande should join the post immediately and report to the Government by e-mail at cp4.mhpds@nic.in.
The Government Order is available on the Government of Maharashtra website www.maharashtra.gov.in.
